videos.description: Kansas State's Cartier Diarra turns good defense into easy offense as he comes up with the steal and rises for an easy two-handed flush.
videos.headline: Diarra steal leads to easy 2-handed flush

videos.description: Texas A&M's Josh Nebo fights for the rebound and muscles his way through contact for an and-1 finish.
videos.headline: Aggies' Nebo finishes through contact for and-1

videos.description: Texas A&M's Savion Flagg hustles back on defense and skies for a nasty rejection on Kansas State's Xavier Sneed.
videos.headline: Flagg gets up for nasty block

videos.description: TJ Starks drives to the hole and throws a sweet pass to Josh Nebo who throws down a powerful slam.
videos.headline: Aggies' Starks dimes Nebo for monster slam

videos.description: Aggies TJ Starks slips past Kansas State defenders and flies for a nasty one-handed flush.
videos.headline: Starks seals the game with vicious slam
